# UX Intelligence

Before **team** (`apps/team`) or **guest booking** (`apps/web`) UI work:

1. Read [docs/UX_INTELLIGENCE_FEED.md](../../docs/UX_INTELLIGENCE_FEED.md) first.
2. Apply the relevant page brief (Clients, Book flow, Checkout, or Dashboard).
3. Cross-check [docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md](../../docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md) for tokens — never use Boulevard purple or generic SaaS blue.
4. Cross-check [docs/BOULEVARD_FEATURE_GAP.md](../../docs/BOULEVARD_FEATURE_GAP.md) so you do not build UI for missing schema/API.
5. Link to the feed section in PR descriptions when UX guidance drove the change.

For ongoing competitor research, follow [docs/AGENT_UX_INTELLIGENCE.md](../../docs/AGENT_UX_INTELLIGENCE.md).
